 den virale kampanjen st\u00e5r blant andre Pia Biermann fra Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10222930.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/thea.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d0ba3f9ee2fff34bdb27b0bf136503f330ca1fa2.jpg?59914691"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Thea (12) ble ikke gift -adressa.no", "N\u00e5dd 100 millioner", "39 000 barnebryllup hver dag", "\u2013 Sterkt, men n\u00f8dvendig virkemiddel"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d0ba3f9ee2fff34bdb27b0bf136503f330ca1fa2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["dagens seremoni", "dag", "kampanje"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kulturkirken jakob", "the independent", "mercur", "buzzfeed", "stopp", "plan norge", "thea", "geir", "huffington post", "trigger", "biermann"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["trondheim", "oslo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["ashton kutcher", "olaf thommessen", "pia biermann", "hege biermann"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10222930.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/thea.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Thea (12) ble ikke gift"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article10222821.ece"}, {"field": "pageclass", "value": ["article"]}, {"field": "publi